trans-unit.source: Specifies the state of an internal Message Queuing transaction.
trans-unit.target: Especifica o estado de uma transação interna do serviço de enfileiramento de mensagens.

trans-unit.source: When an instance of the <xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueueTransaction> class has been created, its <xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueueTransaction.Status%2A> property is set by the constructor to `Initialized`.
trans-unit.target: Quando uma instância do <xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueueTransaction>classe tiver sido criada, seu <xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueueTransaction.Status%2A>propriedade é definida pelo construtor para `Initialized`.</xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueueTransaction.Status%2A> </xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueueTransaction>

trans-unit.source: After a transaction has begun, but before it is committed or rolled back, the <xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueueTransaction.Status%2A> is `Pending`.
trans-unit.target: Depois que uma transação foi iniciada, mas antes de ser confirmada ou revertida, o <xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueueTransaction.Status%2A>é `Pending`.</xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueueTransaction.Status%2A>

trans-unit.source: The transaction has been aborted and all participants have been notified.
trans-unit.target: A transação foi anulada e todos os participantes foram notificados.

trans-unit.source: The transaction has been committed and all participants have been notified.
trans-unit.target: A transação foi confirmada e todos os participantes foram notificados.

trans-unit.source: It has not yet been started.
It has not yet been either committed or rolled back.
trans-unit.target: Ainda não tenha sido seja confirmada ou revertida.
